News Releases, Media Advisories

Mary 12, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON FRIENDS OF WEINER
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Friends of Weiner (NY 9th District). This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on Friends of Weiner
